Product: ThermoPro TP55 Digital Hygrometer Indoor Thermometer
Date: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
Reviews: We have a very expensive Carrier 'smart' thermostat that consistently overstates the temperature and understates the humidity.  It caused our humidifier to be over-used and made the house too moist.  Unfortunately, I did not get these meters in time to beat the expiration of the thermostat's warranty, but the technician was able to 'fool' it to do less humidification.  Side by side these meters agree 99% of the time.
